---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Lifestyle Experiences" description="Enhance your journey with spa & wellness, fine dining, and beach club experiences that elevate every moment of your Bali transformation.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-137 flex items-center justify-center bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-900/60 via-stone-900/40 to-stone-900/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540555700478-4be289fbecef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-animate text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Lifestyle Experiences</p>
      <h1 class="hero-animate hero-animate-delay-1 font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-stone-50 leading-tight">
        The Art of<br/>Living Well
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="prose-luxury">
        <p>
          A transformative journey requires more than profound experiences—it 
          requires the space to integrate them. The moments between adventures, 
          the evenings after ceremonies, the mornings before exploration—these 
          too are part of your journey. We ensure they are as considered and 
          beautiful as everything else.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Spa & Wellness -->
  <section id="spa-wellness" class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-137">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Body & Spirit</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-6">Spa & Wellness</h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-lg italic text-stone-700">
              Where ancient healing traditions meet contemporary luxury, and 
              every treatment is a journey inward.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">Why It Matters</h3>
            <p>
              Transformation is not only of the mind and spirit—it is of the body. 
              The physical vessel that carries you through this journey deserves 
              care that honors its role. Balinese healing traditions understand 
              this deeply, treating body and soul as inseparable.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">The Emotional Value</h3>
            <p>
              After a day of trekking sacred mountains or participating in 
              powerful ceremonies, the body needs restoration. But more than 
              physical relief, spa experiences offer integration—time for the 
              experiences of the day to settle into your being, for insights 
              to crystallize, for transformation to take root.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">How We Enhance Your Journey</h3>
            <p>
              We curate wellness experiences that align with your journey's 
              intention. Traditional Balinese massage in private pavilions 
              overlooking rice terraces. Healing rituals that combine ancient 
              techniques with modern understanding. Yoga sessions with masters 
              who have practiced for decades. Sound healing in sacred spaces. 
              Each experience chosen to support your transformation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fine Dining -->
  <section id="fine-dining" class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Culinary Art</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-6">Fine Dining</h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-lg italic text-stone-700">
              Where every meal tells a story of the land, the sea, and the 
              hands that prepared it with devotion.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">Why It Matters</h3>
            <p>
              Food in Bali is never merely sustenance—it is offering, art, and 
              connection. The island's culinary traditions reflect its spiritual 
              philosophy: that nourishment of the body is inseparable from 
              nourishment of the soul. Every ingredient carries energy, every 
              preparation is an act of intention.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">The Emotional Value</h3>
            <p>
              A meal shared in the right setting, prepared with the right 
              intention, becomes a memory that stays with you forever. The 
              sunset dinner overlooking the Indian Ocean. The private feast 
              in a village home. The tasting menu that takes you on a journey 
              through Bali's diverse culinary heritage. These are not meals—
              they are experiences that nourish something deeper than hunger.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">How We Enhance Your Journey</h3>
            <p>
              We arrange dining experiences that become highlights of your 
              journey. Private tables at Bali's most celebrated restaurants. 
              Chef's table experiences where you witness culinary artistry 
              firsthand. Traditional Balinese feasts prepared by families who 
              have cooked for royalty. Farm-to-table experiences where you 
              harvest ingredients before they become your meal. Each dining 
              moment curated to complement your day's experiences.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-137 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beach Clubs -->
  <section id="beach-clubs" class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-137">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">Coastal Luxury</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-6">Beach Clubs</h2>
          <div class="divider mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-lg italic text-stone-700">
              Where the rhythm of the waves meets the pulse of refined leisure, 
              and every moment is an invitation to simply be.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">Why It Matters</h3>
            <p>
              Even the most meaningful journey requires moments of pure pleasure—
              time to simply exist in beauty without purpose or agenda. Bali's 
              coastline offers some of the world's most spectacular settings 
              for this kind of conscious leisure, where luxury meets the 
              elemental power of the sea.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">The Emotional Value</h3>
            <p>
              There is a particular quality of peace that comes from watching 
              the sun set over the Indian Ocean from a perfectly positioned 
              daybed, a carefully crafted cocktail in hand, the day's adventures 
              settling into memory. This is not escape—it is integration. The 
              space between experiences where transformation quietly deepens.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-900 pt-4">How We Enhance Your Journey</h3>
            <p>
              We secure access to Bali's most exclusive coastal venues—the 
              private cabanas, the reserved sunset positions, the experiences 
              that ordinary visitors cannot access. Whether you seek the 
              sophisticated energy of Seminyak's legendary beach clubs or the 
              serene seclusion of hidden coastal retreats, we ensure your 
              moments of leisure are as considered as your moments of discovery.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Integration -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Complete Experience</p>
      <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-12">
        Luxury as Integration
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <p>
          These lifestyle experiences are not additions to your journey—they 
          are essential elements of it. The spa treatment that helps your body 
          process the morning's trek. The fine dining experience that becomes 
          a celebration of the day's discoveries. The beach club afternoon 
          that provides space for reflection before the evening's ceremony.
        </p>
        <p>
          We weave these moments into your journey with the same intention we 
          bring to every other element. Nothing is incidental. Everything serves 
          your transformation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540555700478-4be289fbecef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/70"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
        Every Moment Matters
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Let us craft a journey where even the spaces between are beautiful.
      </p>
      <a href="/begin" class="btn-luxury-outline">Begin Your Journey</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
